Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So young...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...yet already writing in monotony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:43.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.37,0:00:45.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Very textbook-like, or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...written for the sake of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:53.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you try to overcome the wall of mediocrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:01:00.16,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Award Celebration"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.25,0:00:56.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Director, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:01:00.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When you've been in the business as long as I have, you can see true value.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What an uninteresting piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:07.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, about the picture we took earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Handa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:13.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's so wrong with my work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.58,0:01:24.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you crazy?! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.78,0:01:27.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Damn him for saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:30.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have a clue what I had to go through!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.45,0:01:31.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.37,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"From: Kawafuji
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.37,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,73)}Sub: None
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:48.37,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,104)}How's the island?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:51.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:53.94,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Taxi"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.71,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Airport
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.71,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}Goto Bus"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.68,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(359,45)}"Buses 1-7 operate 6/14-7/31
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.68,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}If flights are canceled, operations may
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.68,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(362,107)}be put on hold, so we ask for your
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.68,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,138)}understanding in this matter."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Barakakodon"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,76)}"Translation: Spirited Child"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.95,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"After you land at Fukue Airport,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.95,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,76)}use the taxi, and once you arrive, contact
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.95,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,107)}the Village Leader, who will be taking care
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.98,0:03:39.95,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,138)}of you. Be sure to mind your manners."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:43.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a lucky one, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:45.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Heck, if I hadn't passed ya,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.59,0:03:48.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,it would've taken ya half a day to get to Nanan'dake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:49.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Would've hadta walk half a day...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I can't understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:56.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! What'd ya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:58.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can't make out a word yer sayin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:03.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I'll just ignore him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There really isn't anything here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:11.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, lookie there! It's the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.28,0:04:14.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How 'bout it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My little tyke is crazy 'bout the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,an' hollers just lookin' at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:28.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How about it...?\NIt's just like any old ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it doesn't look nice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,because my mind isn't at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:36.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,M-My ribs...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.14,0:04:39.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,'Bout as far I'm gonna take ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.01,0:04:41.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got my fields a waitin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Young man, it's not 'cause you ain't calm or nothin'
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,that the ocean don't look nice to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be cloudy in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:54.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:57.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya gotta watch that there ocean when it's rough and tumblin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.63,0:04:59.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya don't get it, do ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:03.87,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Kijima Transport"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:04.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa-{\i1}san{\i0}! Kijima Transport here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:15.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:17.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm from Kijima Transport!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:22.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This should be all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:26.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, aren't you going to help me carry these in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... We don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:31.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,'Scuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:35.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Service sure takes a nosedive without any competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.83,0:05:42.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you're... the Village Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been tiring coming from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here, the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:50.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there any buses or taxis here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bus running once a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:56.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You can call a taxi, but there aren't many here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:00.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you need to go to the shopping district,\NI'll lend you my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.05,0:06:03.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, can you please leave me alone for a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to concentrate on my calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:07.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:11.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here, pass me the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:13.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take all the time you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:15.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry about food, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:28.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, no one is supposed to be living here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:33.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The place feels like it's been lived in...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:39.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's... It's just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--A seal?!\N--Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a plain old seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:07:00.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A squat toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.19,0:07:08.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never used a balanced flue before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You crank it like this to turn the fire on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:21.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is where I'm going to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:32.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.19,0:07:42.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be something in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You found me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Village Leader! Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of the village brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:58.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they used this place as a base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:02.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Base...?\N--Oh, a colony. Colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:04.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, that's harder to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I did tell her to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:09.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nii-{\i1}chan{\i0}, you a Junon Boy? [Junon Boy: "a cool, handsome man"]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:13.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Hey, Naru! It's rude to speak like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:16.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Miwa-{\i1}nee{\i0} said that a Junon Boy is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:20.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-{\i1}chan{\i0} is cool, so he's a Junon Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:25.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so, but he's actually a master calligrapher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:27.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Village Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A Junon Boy who can also write!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:31.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:33.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru thinks he's a Junon Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to start with, he's not young enough to be a "boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But the people on TV fake their age, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:42.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--That's what Miwa-{\i1}nee{\i0} said.\N--Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:46.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure faking their age is part of their work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:49.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Cowboys can be "boys" even if they're middle-aged!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:56.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.\NShe's really hard to reason with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can you please get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Locked...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This place, a "base"? What a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'm lucky that the place was ready to live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:19.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...! Naru wants to write too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you get in...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just because he won...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He spat on the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's basically dead in the world of calligraphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's so rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:44.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to him.\NEveryone will think you're like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get involved with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Four Seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,73)}Perfect Indifference
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,107)}Self-Respect
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.82,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,135)}Amidst Enemies"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I can't concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a kettle in this house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:10:00.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, you need to eat the corn treats stacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.86,0:10:04.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm overweight, so I'm fine eating them one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:06.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey.\N--Wha--?! Handa-{\i1}sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Want some finger-corns?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Rolly-rolly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:14.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new move! A new move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Naru!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Show me how you did that!\N--I can't work like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:21.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Focus... Focus. Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.62,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,42)}"Kotoishi Naru"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:27.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! Pretty good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who said you could write?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, loosen up, Junon Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:35.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a Junon Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:40.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like your name, "Kotoishi Naru,"\NI have a name too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know Naru's name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:44.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You must be one of them mind readers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:48.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm stupid? Or are you just stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naru knows, too! Junon Boy's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.75,0:10:55.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well... good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:56.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.82,0:10:58.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.32,0:11:01.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The Village Leader was sayin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's one archaic effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Junon Takeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.86,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,42)}"Handa Seishu"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:13.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Handa Seishu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:16.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Junon aside, where'd you get the "Takeo" from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a middle schooler's pen name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:20.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pseudonym!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:29.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Sensei writes so neat. You're so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:34.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the school teacher's writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Already writing in monotony...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.29,0:11:41.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Very textbook-like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:43.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What an uninteresting piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! The Village Leader is gonna bring dinner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Why're you doing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It looked so nice, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:53.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Like you'd understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to make it seem like you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.31,0:11:56.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:11:58.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Getting all mad because she was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:17.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was so immature...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.26,0:12:21.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Going to the island? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:25.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My old man said for me to cool myself off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:30.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Said I'm lacking something as a human, never mind a calligrapher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The heck are you laughing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:39.85,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,45)}"Kawafuji Fine Arts"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You punched an old man who uses a cane.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no condolences for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:40.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should just apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:42.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:45.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That geezer and my old man know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:48.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being true to the basics?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:53.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is doing calligraphy fun when you feel that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:59.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The fundamentals are the most beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:01.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:14.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,♪...the most important thing... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:17.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the "most important thing"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.32,0:13:19.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She heard me singing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:22.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's the most important thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:23.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:24.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:27.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Sensei say sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:33.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who said something that Sensei didn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.07,0:13:36.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So I tried to write it again, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:40.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't write like Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:51.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:53.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:57.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to apologize for...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:06.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So happy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:08.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy you're not angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:13.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Saying sorry is so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.71,0:14:16.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad I said sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:17.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for yelling at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:19.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.29,0:14:24.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.93,0:14:26.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:32.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You did really good writing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. It was easy to copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:38.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei's writing is just like a textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, natural reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:52.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know why I got mad, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This was just for practice, so you could've thrown...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:07.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You did it first to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.51,0:15:14.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sen--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me! I thought you croaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,With how heavy my clothes are, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, you city folks don't know a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:30.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See, you have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:36.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, close the neck part of the shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:39.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then get air in through the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:47.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! I can't believe I'm surprised over this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:57.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you swim in deep waters like that all the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:58.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:01.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The fearsome power of kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! I'll show you something neat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:05.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:09.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you climb that wall, you can see a super-duper sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:15.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. You're going to climb this breakwater?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.84,0:16:18.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Gotta climb to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.01,0:16:22.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to see a thing through all these clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta climb to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:31.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't try, you won't find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:37.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No problem, I'm okay. I just rushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:44.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry on up, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:49.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't climb this wall, you're not gonna see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:55.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...try to overcome the wall of mediocrity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:17.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See? Pretty, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.44,0:17:24.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:35.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, yer back, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--The first villager...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:38.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:41.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa? Your grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:42.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:44.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Better hurry or we're gonna break open them boxes for ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ya just moved here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...so we're here ta help ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.17,0:17:54.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:18:00.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyo, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:03.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Mighty far place you came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.58,0:18:07.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going in, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:08.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.92,0:18:11.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! Hurry, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:14.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did your grandpa call for everyone to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:15.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:20.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone saw the mover's truck and came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not like we get plenty of folks moving here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and I can't have them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a handsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:34.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:36.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:38.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is Naru's friend, Hina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina's super shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:48.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So I shouldn't talk to her too much, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.99,0:18:54.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina wants Sensei's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see... Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hina cries when she's happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she's hard to handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:06.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Butt... stab!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:10.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were wide open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:15.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We said at the class meeting that butt-stabbing isn't allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:17.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, smoke face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:19.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:22.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You just can't get through to brats like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.19,0:19:23.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And this here is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:30.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's the head teacher for the school branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:31.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hi there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:35.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, there's nothing funnier than seeing a handsome guy being shamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:41.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, we can just put them in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:43.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:57.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! See you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:59.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Kawafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:42.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now I kind of get why my old man sent me to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I come up with something good, I'll submit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask for your help then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.31,0:20:49.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Also... can you apologize to the Director for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do it myself? I can't do that yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? This island?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:04.89,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(361,44)}"Ease, Comfort, Relief"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:04.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:43.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I brought... champon noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.86,0:22:49.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Freaky.
